Package universum.studios.android.fragment.annotation.handler

Provides group of annotation handler implementations used across the Fragments library for annotations processing and handling.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionBarFragmentAnnotationHandler
    A FragmentAnnotationHandler extended interface for annotation handlers from the Fragments library that are used to handle processing of annotations attached to classes derived from the ActionBar Fragment classes provided by this library.
    AnnotationHandler
    Base interface for annotation handlers from the Fragments library that are used to handle processing of annotations attached to classes derived from base classes provided by this library or to theirs fields.
    FragmentAnnotationHandler
    An AnnotationHandler extended interface for annotation handlers from the Fragments library that are used to handle processing of annotations attached to classes derived from BaseFragment class provided by this library.
    FragmentFactoryAnnotationHandler
    An AnnotationHandler extended interface for annotation handlers from the Fragments library that are used to handle processing of annotations attached to classes derived from BaseFragmentFactory class provided by this library.
    WebFragmentAnnotationHandler
    An ActionBarFragmentAnnotationHandler extended interface for annotation handlers from the Fragments library that are used to handle processing of annotations attached to classes derived from WebFragment class provided by this library.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionBarAnnotationHandlers
    An AnnotationHandlers implementation providing AnnotationHandler instances for ActionBar associated fragments and classes.
    AnnotationHandlers
    Base factory and cache for AnnotationHandler instances for a specific classes from the Fragments library.
    BaseAnnotationHandlers
    An AnnotationHandlers implementation providing AnnotationHandler instances for classes from the fragments base package.
    BaseManagementAnnotationHandlers
    An AnnotationHandlers implementation providing AnnotationHandler instances for base management associated fragments and classes.
    WebAnnotationHandlers
    An AnnotationHandlers implementation providing AnnotationHandler instances for web associated fragments and classes.
